## Error Path Behavior

- **Partial success** (org resolved, project fails): `resolveOrg()` sets the org tag before project resolution throws — org tag survives on the error event.
- **Complete failure** (no org found): No tags set — correct.
- **Explicit but nonexistent project**: Tags are set before any downstream API call (e.g., `fetchProjectId`), so error events carry the user-typed org/project for debugging.

